def no_lines(field)
    unless field.nil?
        return field.gsub("\n", " ")
    end
end

def country_list(countries)
list = []
   countries.each do |country|
      list.push(country.name)
   end
   country_list = list.join("; ")
   country_list
end

require 'csv'
resource_file = "#{Rails.root}/log/ind_studes_resources.csv"
